fulltitle: Covert Action and US Foreign Policy (1992)
title: Covert Action and US Foreign Policy (1992)
description:
MAY 4, 1992 | The task force on Covert Action recently released the results of their investigation into U.S. covert action. Members of the task force discussed their recommendations for future U.S. foreign policy at this news conference.

ORIGINAL: https://www.c-span.org/video/?25910-1/covert-action-us-foreign-policy
